excerpt: Celebrated beach area featuring scenic cliffs with ocean views & a peaceful atmosphere.
detail_description: Yarada Beach is a serene and picturesque destination in Visakhapatnam, also known as Vizag. Surrounded by scenic cliffs and offering stunning ocean views, this beach provides a peaceful atmosphere for travelers seeking an escape from city life. excerpt: Submarine museum & former navy vessel offering cabin tours by retired military personnel.
detail_description: The VMRDA INS Kursura Submarine Museum, located on RK Beach in Visakhapatnam, is a popular tourist attraction. This museum features the INS Kurusura, a Russian-built submarine that was inducted into the Indian Navy in 1969 and decommissioned in 2001 after 31 years of service. It is the first submarine museum in Asia and the second in the world.

Visitors can explore the park through guided safaris to gain insights into the unusual fauna and participate in conservation education initiatives.
